Compiling GPUMD

Statement:
This tutorial is not guaranteed to work flawlessly on all machines.
Please email the author if you have any questions.

After compiling GPUMD, one should install the NVIDIA drivers and CUDA.
The version of CUDA should match with NVIDIA drivers.
The version NVIDIA drivers should match with your computer.

Installation tutorial:
Read the 'Compile GPUMD' part of:
https://github.com/Kick-H/GPUMD/blob/master/README.md
